  "summary": {
    "en": "A 69-piece kids tent building kit and connector ball tent set with blue rods, mixed-color connector balls, clips, storage bag, and printed tent blanket.",
    "zh": "69件 LONDY Little Explorer 套装，配置蓝色杆、混色连接球、夹子、收纳袋和印花帐篷布。"
  },
  "description": {
    "en": [
      "The 69-piece LONDY Little Explorer set pairs blue PP rods with mixed-color connector balls for a compact fort building kit, connector ball tent, and tent-style builds.",
      "The box includes rods, connector balls, purple clips, a printed tent blanket, handbook, PE warning bag, and storage bag.",
      "Packed set price is $17.13. Package reference is 45 x 9 x 35 cm, with about 2.4 kg quoted weight.",
      "Printed blankets and storage bags can be customized for brand orders that need a make a fort toy or kids tent building kit entry SKU."
    ],
    "zh": [
      "69件 LONDY Little Explorer 采用蓝色 PP 杆和混色连接球，适合搭建小型堡垒和帐篷框架。",
      "套装包含杆件、连接球、紫色夹子、印花帐篷布、说明书、PE 警示袋和收纳袋。",
      "单盒合计价格 $17.13，包装参考为 45 x 9 x 35 cm，报价重量约 2.4 kg。",
      "印花毯和收纳袋可按品牌需求定制。"
    ]
  },
